**Launch is scheduled to block 5_931_714 (~ 19PM CET)**  
**The first auction will take place on epoch 16431 which is the SAME epoch in which block 5_931_714 is in**

---

### Final Design (v1.0.0)
The design that will be implemented in v1.0.0 will **NOT** be a bond curve which was the design previously proposed.  
We have decided after some discussions that allowing miners to minimize alpha adquisition price is the way to go. Both options had its strengths and weakenesses but lets give this a try.  
This means auctions will occur **each epoch**, have a **total reward of 148 sn73 alpha (361*0.41) ** , and miners will get weights proportionally to how much **total post-slippage value** they sent to coldkey from their **registered miner coldkey.**
Miners will have to compete for the 148 sn73 αlpha without sending too much and reacting to what other miners send. Game theory at its best.

---
### First Auctions
All validators have been notified and most should be running the last version. However, we recommend playing "safe" the first couple of auctions. Gain intuition, dont ape, watch the auction progress etc. Some alpha could be loss if validators fail to work properly as default behaviour is to burn all alpha. Wait till you see validators setting NON-ZERO weights. 

---
### Scripts & Tools
Although miners **DONT** have to deploy any neuron (`miner.py`), we have prepared some usefull scripts and tools (located in `scripts/miner`) that can be used to track the state of the auction, auto-bid, etc. Miners are free to just register and send alpha manually but we hope this scripts will come handy to them.
You have auction_watch.py and leaderboard.py. the first is an Auto-bidder script and the second a leaderboard to track current state of auction. Pls take into account is miners job to actually decide the strategy of how to send the alpha and this are just BASE scripts. 

For more info check https://github.com/fx-integral/metahash/blob/main/docs/miner.md

---

### Website
As you have probably already seen, we are preparing a treasury page (<https://metahash73.com/treasury>) and soon we will have a leaderboard page (for miners) and an **"auctions"** page to track past auctions and even a live mode to see the current auction.

---

### Support
Any problem miners have our DMs are opened and we will be connected and available to help solve any problem or doubt. Miners will probably need some time to understand and adapt to the game theory mechanics that will happen in this subnet. Hopefully everyone will gain value: **MetaHash will be able to aduqire discounted alpha and grow a treasury and miners will gain liquidity OTC.**
